Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.60,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Tired of seeing all the wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.60,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I just wanna take a step further
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.39,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}For you, I could be a whole lot stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.00,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Can you face it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:33.00,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Living this history
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.21,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.76,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Fantasy is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:44.60,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I just want you to face state of uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.76,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I'd been seein' so many people taking lives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.93,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Tryna be different, little babies crying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.10,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}So many innocents, thinkin' it's commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.27,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Gathering little dreams, fighting till the end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.48,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}With a sharp blade, I'll be cuttin' through hate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.73,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Had enough of all this, hydrate everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.61,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}What I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.83,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}What you've done can't be erased
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:11.33,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Cross over
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:15.29,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}All you've brought is hardship but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.42,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Hope is still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.18,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I face myself now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.44,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}To end this tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.36,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Surely and certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.98,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Look back and see truth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.24,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}You'll realize less is more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.95,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Leave your emptiness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.03,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I'd been seein' so many souls searchin'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.04,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Justice used to be more nursing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.46,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}What are we doing? More blood shedding
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.62,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Washing hearts with pain'll make a better day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.75,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Losing faith, clinging to our selfish truths
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.00,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Choosing roads, living in our own rules
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.01,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}All for what? To protect loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:01.88,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Never surrender
