Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.35,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}你的行动都不会消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:15.02,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}跨越困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.98,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}尽管你经历过艰难险阻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.65,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但希望依然不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.86,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}希望依然不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.82,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}为了自己的梦想而发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.87,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}希望依然不灭
